<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Culture characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Colonies growing slowly, attaining 30 mm diam. after 2 weeks at 27 °C under dark, circular, with even margin, floccose at the centre, drift white at margin, light greenish at centre, dark from below.</paragraph>
